  "question": "A man with lung cancer and bone metastasis in the thoracic spinal vertebral bodies, sustains a pathological fracture at the level of T4. The fracture is unstable and the spinal cord is severely compressed at this level. Which of the findings below will not be present 6 weeks after injury?",
