  "question": "A 72 year old lady falls and lands on her left hip. She attends the emergency department and is given some paracetamol by the junior doctor and discharged. Several months later she presents with ongoing pain and discomfort of the hip. Avascular necrosis of the femoral head is suspected. Which of the following features is least likely to be present?",
