  "question": "A 55-year-old male with a history of chronic pancreatitis secondary to alcohol is being managed conservatively as an out-patient. It is decided to assess the exocrine function of his pancreas prior to nutritional interventions. Which of the following techniques is the best assessment technique for the exocrine status of the pancreas? Select one answer only.",
