  "question": "6 months following transplantation a patient is seen in clinic with a mild swelling and tenderness in the region of the transplant. Their renal function has deteriorated. A computed tomography (CT) scan demonstrates a collection between the lower pole of the kidney and bladder. Select the most likely complication for this case.",
