  "question": "An 85-year-old man is found at laparotomy to have a perforated gastric\nulcer high on the lesser curve. His past medical history includes COAD\n(chronic obstructive airways disease) and angina. Select the most\nappropriate option from the list below for the treatment of this patients.",
