  "question": "A 40-year-old man is involved in a road traffic accident and sustains\nneck injury with C4/C5 dislocation. On examination he has loss of motor\nfunction on one side and loss of pain and temperature sensation on the\ncontralateral side. Which spinal cord syndrome is associated with these\nfindings?",
