  "question": "A 31-year-old woman underwent primary varicose vein surgery of her left lower limb 2 weeks ago. She came back to the follow up clinic complaining of pain and paraesthesia in the skin of the medial aspect of her left leg and foot. Which nerve has been injured during the procedure?",
