  "question": "A 53-year-old woman has fallen onto her outstretched right hand, result-ing in an undisplaced fracture of the distal radius and ulna. She was previously fit and well. She wants to know how long it will take for the fracture to heal.\nHow long would you expect this fracture to take to heal?",
