  "question": "A new blood test has been produced to help diagnose suspected tumours of the membranous urethra. Of a study sample of 100 patients, 20 are known to have cancer of the membranous urethra. The blood test suggested that 30 people had the tumour, but of these only 15 were true positives. What is the positive predictive value of this test?",
