  "question": "A 24-year- old woman with no past medical history of note comes to see you at the GP practice complaining of a 2-day history of urinary fre-quency together with a stinging sensation on passing urine. She is sys-temically well.Which of the following organisms is most likely to have caused her symptoms?",
