  "question": "An elderly gentleman presents to your clinic with progressive weight loss, dysphagia and several episodes of haemetamesis. An upper gastrointestinal endoscopy reveals a fungating growth in his distal oesophagus. Which of the following statements is correct regarding oesophageal carcinoma? Select one answer only.",
