  "question": "You are seeing a patient in the joint oncology clinic who is about to start a course of radiotherapy for adjuvant treatment of breast cancer. Whilst waiting for the oncologist she asks you questions regarding radiotherapy as a general principle. Which of the following statements is correct regarding radiotherapy? Select one answer only.",
