  "id": 206132,
  "question": "Your team has recently performed a right mastectomy and level 3 axillary node clearance for a 43year-old lady. Histology reveals a 43 mm grade 3 carcinoma with 13/15 nodes positive. The tumor is ER/PR/Her-2 positive. Following discussion at the MDT she has been recommended for radiotherapy, chemotherapy, Herceptin and endocrine manipulation in due course. Which of the following statements is true regarding chemotherapy? Select one answer only.",
